{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":703333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[25],"categories_output":[{"ID":25,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e7%90%90%e7%a2%8e","name":"生活琐碎","term_taxonomy_id":25,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":25}],"tags":[155,156,119],"tags_output":[{"ID":155,"slug":"%e4%ba%ba%e7%94%9f","name":"人生","term_taxonomy_id":155,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":156,"slug":"%e8%81%8c%e4%b8%9a","name":"职业","term_taxonomy_id":156,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":4},{"ID":119,"slug":"%e8%81%8c%e5%9c%ba","name":"职场","term_taxonomy_id":119,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":6}],"thumbnail":[],"thumbnail_mini":[],"thumbnail_retina":[],"thumbnail_full":[],"date_day":"01","date_month":"11","date_month_e":"November","date_year":"2017","date_weekday":"Wednesday","title":"浅谈自己的职场感悟「循环」","excerpt":"自从毕业开始工作的第一天，我们都面临这么一个《循环》，自己的真实感受，顺便画成了一个简单的图示，为了让自己把自己看得更清晰。当你毕业踏上工作的第一天你就已经陷入了“选择”这个无限循环中恰恰多数时候...","content":"<p>自从毕业开始工作的第一天，我们都面临这么一个《循环》，自己的真实感受，顺便画成了一个简单的图示，为了让自己把自己看得更清晰。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/static-remote/files/e9a5e277f0e458f82addfcdd-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadseaefefaddfcddjpg.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"/static-remote/files/e9a5e277f0e458f82addfcdd-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadseaefefaddfcddjpg.jpg\" alt=\"浅谈自己的职场感悟---《循环》\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>当你毕业踏上工作的第一天<br />\n你就已经陷入了“选择”这个无限循环中<br />\n恰恰多数时候，这5个循环节点都存在互相排斥性<br />\n当然也可以选择性的融合它们，<br />\n想要全部融合不产生排斥，基本是不可能做到的。</p>\n<p>如此循环，或好或坏，你会发现真正的你：<br />\n那就是勇气、胆量和意志力</p>\n<p>如此循环，或好或坏，它们都有一个共性：<br />\n那就是风险<br />\n循规蹈矩的风险<br />\n自由的风险<br />\n高成就的风险<br />\n无追求的风险<br />\n...</p>\n<p>如何选择，如何循环自己的人生，如何走出这个循环，<br />\n是一瞬间，也是一辈子的抉择。</p>\n<p>做出一个合适的选择，非常难。<br />\n但是，当你想通了某些事，选择可以很容易。<br />\n当你无法想通的那段时间，你会非常艰难，甚至可能自暴自弃。<br />\n没关系，因为你一定可以做出选择。</p>\n<p>是否你也有过和我一样的感受呢？</p>\n","slug":"e9a4d248480202d17feb6f4c","prev":[{"ID":693333,"title":"5个可能会阻碍设计师未来发展的危险信号","excerpt":"当今各种互联网产品的竞争已经非常激烈，现成的各种软件、APP、框架、Web应用、Kit、主题插件的提供商的数量正在以极大的速度增长，面对这些不可避免的趋势和现状，设计师不得不思考未来自己的职业发展方向。这篇文章时我站在自己的角度，对未来可能面对的比较明显的危险信号做一个总结和表述，仅代表自己的观点，供大家参考。","slug":"08b5f8d6157f93072cf64289","post_date":"2017-08-13 16:46:50","post_date_gmt":"2017-08-13 16:46:50","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_7271c53de137bf3c24bfa5b6-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcdebfcbfabxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_7271c53de137bf3c24bfa5b6-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcdebfcbfabxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_7271c53de137bf3c24bfa5b6-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomcdebfcbfabxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":713333,"title":"回顾我在2017年的网页设计之路的思维转变过程","excerpt":"做网页设计也有一些年头了，在这个复杂的人生历程中，我有了一个和以往不同的思维方式的转变，多多少少，也会让自己的行为方式，学习技巧，职场期望等作出一些调整。","slug":"a98c5926a20eb417f5e79c64","post_date":"2017-11-08 13:19:50","post_date_gmt":"2017-11-08 13:19:50","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_16e3e75d1311c756a5a52042-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomeedcaaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_16e3e75d1311c756a5a52042-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomeedcaaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_16e3e75d1311c756a5a52042-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomeedcaaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2017-11-01 00:24:09","post_date_gmt":"2017-11-01 00:24:09","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2022-11-17 02:16:09","post_modified_gmt":"2022-11-17 02:16:09","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"